PresentationTable.name: Base Facts
PresentationTable.Description: This folder contains all the base facts like Revenue, Quantity, Target, Headcount and so on. All the metrics in this folder have the aggregation type as Sum unless explicitly specified.

PresentationColumn.name: 1- Revenue
PresentationColumn.Description:
Help : Revenue data. Sources from Revenue physical column in 'Sample Revenue Fact' table joining to time using Billed time.
- Returns sum of data over any selected dimensions

PresentationColumn.name: 2- Billed Quantity
PresentationColumn.Description:
Help : Billed Quantity data. Sources from Units physical column in 'Sample Revenue Fact' table joining to time using Billed time.
- Returns sum of data over any selected dimension

PresentationColumn.name: 3- Discount Amount
PresentationColumn.Description:
Help : Discount Amount data. Sources from Discount Value physical column in 'Sample Revenue Fact' table joining to time using Billed time.
- Returns sum of data over any selected dimension

PresentationColumn.name: 4- Paid Amount
PresentationColumn.Description:
Help : Paid Amount data. Sources from Revenue column in 'Sample Revenue Fact' table joining to time using Paid time.
- Returns sum of data over any selected dimensions

PresentationColumn.name: 5- Target Revenue
PresentationColumn.Description:
Help : Target Revenue data. Sources from Revenue physical column in 'Sample Targets Fact' table joining to time using Billed time. Target Revenue is available at the Month level grain.
- Returns sum of data over any selected dimension

PresentationColumn.name: 6- Target Quantity
PresentationColumn.Description:
Help : Target Quantity data. Sources from Units physical column in 'Sample Targets Fact' table joining to time using Billed time. Target Quantity is available at the Month level grain.
- Returns sum of data over any selected dimension

PresentationColumn.name: 7- Shipped Amount
PresentationColumn.Description:
Help : Booked Amount data. Sources from Dollars column in FactsRev table joining to time using Booked time.
- Returns sum of data over any selected dimensions

PresentationColumn.name: 8- Booked Amount
PresentationColumn.Description:
Help : Booked Amount data. Sources from Dollars column in FactsRev table joining to time using Booked time.
- Returns sum of data over any selected dimensions
